1.0.name: wordpress/bookmark-me
1.0.description:
A simple and light plugin to add social bookmarks buttons to post and pages. I'm focusing in collecting non-english bookmarks services.

Please help me to collect non english social bookmark sites: I cannot read other languages than english and italian. Send me your sites to satollo@gmail.com.
